    <title>mysql-net/MySqlConnector - Releases - 2023-11-14</title>
    <id>https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector#2023-11-14</id>
    <link href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector" />
    <updated>2023-11-15T00:05:04Z</updated>
    <content type="html">
                &lt;div&gt;
                    
                        &lt;article&gt;
                            &lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/releases/tag/2.3.0"&gt;2.3.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
                            &lt;div&gt;
                                &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support .NET 8.0.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mark some serialization APIs as &lt;code&gt;[Obsolete]&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement &lt;code&gt;DbBatchCommand.CreateParameter&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1831133009" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1352" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1352/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1352"&gt;#1352&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimizations: Use &lt;code&gt;IUtf8SpanFormattable&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Ascii.FromUtf16&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Guid(bigEndian: true)&lt;/code&gt; constructor, argument-throwing helpers, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support .NET Framework 4.8 (&lt;code&gt;net48&lt;/code&gt;) TFM: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="5535038" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/discussions/1355" data-hovercard-type="discussion" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/discussions/1355/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/discussions/1355"&gt;#1355&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This allows &lt;code&gt;TlsVersion = TLSv1.3&lt;/code&gt; to be used on .NET Framework 4.8.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drop support for .NET 4.6.1 and .NET Core 3.1: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="443035395" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/636" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/636/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/636"&gt;#636&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1515215353" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1273" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1273/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1273"&gt;#1273&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;.NET 4.6.1 support ended on 26 April 2022, and .NET Core 3.1 on 13 December 2022.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The minimum supported versions are now .NET Framework 4.6.2 and .NET 6.0, although other frameworks should be supported via &lt;code&gt;netstandard2.0&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource&lt;/code&gt; is now available for all TFMs, not just .NET 7.0: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1512284124" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1269" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1269/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1269"&gt;#1269&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This provides a single place to configure a MySQL connection and makes it easier to register &lt;code&gt;MySqlConnection&lt;/code&gt; with dependency injection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSourceBuilder&lt;/code&gt; class to configure &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource&lt;/code&gt; instances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource.Name&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSourceBuilder.UseName&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microsoft.Extensions.Logging is now used as the core logging abstraction: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1092084374" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1110" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1110/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1110"&gt;#1110&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;MySqlConnectorLogManager.Provider&lt;/code&gt; can still be used to add a logging destination, but it is now deprecated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSourceBuilder.UseLoggerFactory&lt;/code&gt; to configure logging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add new MySqlConnector.DependencyInjection package: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1513092090" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1271" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1271/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1271"&gt;#1271&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;MySqlConnection&lt;/code&gt; can be registered with dependency injection by using &lt;code&gt;builder.Services.AddMySqlDataSource(connectionString)&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This also configures logging automatically.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expose connection pool metrics: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="318746327" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/491" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/491/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/491"&gt;#491&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remove &lt;code&gt;COM_MULTI&lt;/code&gt; protocol support: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="808051418" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/946" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/946/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/946"&gt;#946&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support &lt;code&gt;ZEROFILL&lt;/code&gt; columns in &lt;code&gt;MySqlDecimal&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1854013854" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1354" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1354/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1354"&gt;#1354&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support higher-precision &lt;code&gt;DateTime&lt;/code&gt; values: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1931487928" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1379" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1379/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1379"&gt;#1379&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;ValueTask&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;MySqlBulkCopy&lt;/code&gt; API for all TFMs: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1878888294" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1364" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1364/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1364"&gt;#1364&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Breaking&lt;/strong&gt; This changes the return type of &lt;code&gt;WriteToServerAsync&lt;/code&gt; from &lt;code&gt;Task&amp;lt;MySqlBulkCopyResult&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;ValueTask&amp;lt;MySqlBulkCopyResult&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on .NET Framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support skipping metadata for prepared statements with MariaDB 10.6 and later: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1649425451" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1301" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1301/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1301"&gt;#1301&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support multiple authentication methods when connecting: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1657778824" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1303" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1303/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1303"&gt;#1303&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support per-query variables for &lt;code&gt;CommandBehavior.SchemaOnly&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;SingleRow&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1680735146" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1312" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1312/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1312"&gt;#1312&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recycle &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataReader&lt;/code&gt; objects: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1522967730" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1277" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1277/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1277"&gt;#1277&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform XA rollback when preparing a transaction fails: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1813882844" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1348" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1348/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1348"&gt;#1348&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement faster parsing for result sets with multiple rows: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1758834963" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1330" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1330/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1330"&gt;#1330&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize parameter encoding for ASCII strings: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1631851752" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1296" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1296/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1296"&gt;#1296&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;TcpClient.ConnectAsync&lt;/code&gt; overload with &lt;code&gt;CancellationToken&lt;/code&gt; on .NET 5.0 and later: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1625252575" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1291" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1291/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1291"&gt;#1291&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix cancellation when using a redirected connection: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1659398906" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1305" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1305/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1305"&gt;#1305&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix &lt;code&gt;MySqlConnection.CloneWith&lt;/code&gt; for connections created from a &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1659661167" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1306" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1306/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1306"&gt;#1306&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work around ephemeral PEM bug on Windows: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1524768149" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1278" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1278/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1278"&gt;#1278&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduce allocations on common code paths.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix bug when column name begins with &lt;code&gt;@&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;MySqlBulkCopy&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1879101419" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1365" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1365/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1365"&gt;#1365&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ignore &lt;code&gt;MySqlDbType&lt;/code&gt; when serializing enum values: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1976761546" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1384" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1384/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1384"&gt;#1384&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix bug that didn't copy &lt;code&gt;MySqlDataSource&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;MySqlConnection.Clone&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1511947230" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1267" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1267/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1267"&gt;#1267&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix version parsing for MariaDB 11.0 and later: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1676743208" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1311" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1311/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1311"&gt;#1311&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix potential error in reallocating an internal buffer when writing ASCII text.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update handling of &lt;code&gt;ActivityStatus&lt;/code&gt; to latest conventions: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1764896711" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1334" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1334/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1334"&gt;#1334&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduce overhead of &lt;code&gt;CommandTimeout&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1772998824" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1338" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1338/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/pull/1338"&gt;#1338&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reword end-of-stream message to be more generic: &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1961645691" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1383" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1383/hovercard" href="https://github.com/mysql-net/MySqlConnector/issues/1383"&gt;#1383&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thanks to &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/gboucher90/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/gboucher90"&gt;@gboucher90&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/JackBOBO/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/JackBOBO"&gt;@JackBOBO&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/Kielek/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/Kielek"&gt;@Kielek&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/rusher/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/rusher"&gt;@rusher&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/stilettk/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/stilettk"&gt;@stilettk&lt;/a&gt; for contributions to this release.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
                            &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;/article&gt;
                    
